== Festivals ==

* January 9-10 - Hatsukonpira Festival
* February 3 - {{ill|Setsubun Festival|ja|節分祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Setsubun Festival|qq=}}
* March - Hachiōji Kitsune Festival
* April - Night Worship Event
* June 30 - {{ill|Ōharae|ja|大祓式|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōharae|qq=}} (Great Purification Ceremony)
* July - Gion Festival
* September 20 - Annual Grand Festival (Featuring geisha performances)
* September (Autumn Equinox) - {{ill|Naki Sumo|ja|泣き相撲|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Naki Sumo|qq=}} (Crying Sumo Festival)
* October - Moon Viewing Festival
* December 31 - Ōharae (Great Purification Ceremony)

